metadata.name: #0639 - It's All Relative
metadata.description: Non-Fungible Tombstones are a collectible NFT project meant to celebrate all things perishable, including the death of your neighbor’s cat, the death of crypto (again), and the end of humanity. Worried that the real world is running out of places for us to put our… leftovers? Well, worry no longer! There’s plenty of metadirt in the metaverse. With 2222 Plots available in 20 Types, there is a space for every kind of collector. Reserve your spot in the virtual graveyard today. And remember folks, you will die!
